32,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"09fa92be-b9d5-11f8-7758-e4ecc49f79eb","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Read Recent from Notion\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"c74b8252-4eac-fc46-fad4-1aba2528613a","name":"Note: Read Recent from Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Trim to Digest Size","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"b7aa1826-614e-73b5-5710-14c074d3ca19","name":"Note: Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Trim to Digest Size\n\nCaps the stream at 15 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Content (AI)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7a78ecdb-90d5-b5bc-70bf-cf554a52ee96","name":"Note: Trim to Digest Size"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Content (AI)\n\nMap-reduce summarization chain — handles long content without blowing the context window.\n\nPorts: ①→ Post Digest to Telegram · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"1f197921-9c23-3a0c-da36-659df5b9cb32","name":"Note: Summarize Content (AI)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Summarize Content (AI)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"cf340f68-b048-16df-da55-2f82d755cfb7","name":"Note: Anthropic Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Telegram\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Archive Digest in Notion · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,520],"id":"f7b0d64f-fffa-f27a-3fc9-1940ec8a649a","name":"Note: Post Digest to Telegram"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Digest in Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Processing Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,520],"id":"fc8cf3c0-dd8d-a8ff-9561-2641416a1341","name":"Note: Archive Digest in Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Sort Documents Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,520],"id":"98921e97-b259-783b-ba67-40a903e6105f","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Documents Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"11d9f17f-f03f-a270-39d9-30ccff581cbc","name":"Note: Sort Documents Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"0ebcd915-ed9c-5112-232f-c1f9548999e1","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3153,520],"id":"52f73904-1884-3a89-d2fa-84f42006358e","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Telegram · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"3649d599-8b1b-8ae0-8a7d-7d11b53be503","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Telegram\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"18676d33-09fb-a9bc-7cdf-8cd003de9440","name":"Note: Send Summary to Telegram"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3153,1540],"id":"c07e8be4-ca47-b3c3-00a7-b3bac42619e2","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,1540],"id":"5a2674db-9d63-f00f-f768-1302b70ecf44","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Distill meeting notes with Notion and Telegram\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDistill meeting notes with Notion and Telegram. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual contracts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Read Recent from Notion → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Post Digest to Telegram → Archive Digest in Notion → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating contracts in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Anthropic API key; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"a98fe2dd-998c-2186-0d21-f4c153593447","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"051e21e5-6029-7486-00b4-02bfdc49f8d5","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"31cfe44d-cd63-20fc-dd92-cd56b0a248ef","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"5878f270-0cdb-3ce9-9ee8-6913130fac43","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your contracts process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"5d9491fa-d5b0-577c-50c9-94878676fecc","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Recent from Notion","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Recent from Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Newest First","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Trim to Digest Size","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Trim to Digest Size":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Anthropic Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Summarize Content (AI)":{"main":[[{"node":"Post Digest to Telegram","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Telegram":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Digest in Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Digest in Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Documents Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Documents Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Telegram","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Telegram":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"b8f7c3f7-3c9b-4b52-8e49-b910af99690e","id":"FDX03505"}